    "name": "QA Test Generator API",
    "description": "Sign up, log in, and exercise the repository, session, agent stream, human-in-the-loop, and coding-run endpoints. Set `githubToken` and `replacementGithubToken` before running repository requests. Login stores `accessToken`, repository creation stores `repositoryId`, session creation stores `repositorySessionId`, and test generation stores `codingRunId`. The repository must be ready before creating a session.",
